{"tid":1549800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」要人啊！！！今次學生做咗咁多嘢 你地唔係唔支持學生啊嘛","createTime":"2019-09-07T12:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T13:36:05.000Z","uid":90425,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"600579855364b02c1247e3cb8070c5566d79ef69","tid":1549800,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"Repost<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">學生哥喺學校搞連儂牆 </span></span><br />\n又罷課  又開學禮嗌口號 又面對啲藍屍教畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地唔係唔幫手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位街坊朝早<br />\n早啲起身落街食早餐<br />\n保護下啲學生 <br />\n費事比狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各區都有唔同人鏈活動</span></span><br />\n各位校友係時候探下啲師弟師妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以拖吓手仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLturQo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLturQo.png&h=04abb001&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eEhbFap.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeEhbFap.png&h=d2f539a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vGLKGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vGLKGd.jpg&h=5a8e45fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1VQbWp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1VQbWp.png&h=01889bac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcJm225.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFcJm225.png&h=c299d5f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RDhCBr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRDhCBr9.jpg&h=51835155&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrgjPNa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrgjPNa.png&h=5a03d1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30Qb3d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30Qb3d.png&h=a287f834&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xMZxqoe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxMZxqoe.jpg&h=e6dee7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yLC3w3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyLC3w3e.jpg&h=5be754b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">學生九月九 一齊手拖手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">學生九月九 一齊手拖手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">學生九月九 一齊手拖手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">學生今次出左咁多力 <br />\n你地唔係唔幫佢地呀？<br />\n學生你地都要嚟幫手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n學生校友assemble ！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ef338e40c47b41e4b12910573847bc3b44aba4d9","tid":1549800,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:42:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af1a8498bb0404295ac58b65799b55248a7cd69d","tid":1549800,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fccb7df056a8a640be2792f568c5351d842a4a64","tid":1549800,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a114be04bf815267def593fd5c78361690dfa81","tid":1549800,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8cf4566b82a7b1dca9714400b98af08c5a0d20b","tid":1549800,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d94c2731e4e0928b3c9cb51fab3afebd90670b0","tid":1549800,"uid":227312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad4b51e44326a74aae2fdcd7aed9c1ef8010c256","tid":1549800,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"9/9 學生手拖手"},{"pid":"90ed7dd72980f28637dc64121287dd08dc4516a4","tid":1549800,"uid":90425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f8acbcd1111f18de1a89140019625db50cd6407","tid":15